Architecture: arm64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: NexusMTA - Termux 64-bit Mail Transfer Agent
 A lightweight Mail Transfer Agent for 64-bit ARM Termux.
 Handles SMTP queue processing and mail routing.

Package: nexus-smtp-termux64
Architecture: arm64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: NexusSMTP - Termux 64-bit SMTP Server
 A robust SMTP server for 64-bit ARM Termux.
 Handles incoming mail submission and routing.

Package: nexus-rmc-termux64
Architecture: arm64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: NexusRMC - Termux 64-bit Remote Mail Client
 A command-line remote mail client with DKIM/DMARC/SPF support.
